          <h2>BETTER REACHABILITY</h2>
          <p>The donors don’t need to transport the foods since we are creating a sub-control system by which the people who are in need will directly collect the food. So we doesn’t have any transportation charges.
             We don’t need to search the needy people, because we are making them to come to us.  Hence it’s a self-sustaining idea! </p>
        </div>

        <div class="c2 col-lg-6">
          <h2>ZERO WASTAGE</h2>
          <p>The important Goal of us is Zero wastage of the food which can be achieved by making sure that the receiver collects the food.
             And we will also set an expiry time limit for the food items before which the receiver should collect the food, so the food items will not be wasted and the donors don’t need to wait for the receiver for a long time. </p>
        </div>
        <div class="c2 col-lg-6">
